- content_for :javascript do 
  != map_javascript_include_tags
#map
:javascript
  var stop_lon = #{@stop_area.lon};
  var stop_lat = #{@stop_area.lat};
  jQuery(document).ready(function(){
     stop_init();
  });
= render :partial => 'shared/respond', :locals => { :instance => @stop_area }
.stop
  .name= @stop_area.description
The following stops are here: 
- @stop_area.stops.each do |stop|
  .stop= link_to(stop.full_name, stop_url(stop))
You can pick up the following routes here:
- @stop_area.routes.each do |route|
  .route= link_to(route.name, route_url(route))
